metadata.name: Zapata
metadata.description: Zapata a is tenacious farmer who grows healthy, organic food in the heart of the metropolis of Madara, despite pollution and drought. He uses traditional and sustainable methods from his ancestors to create urban gardens and rooftop farms. He not only provides healthy food but also preserves his culture and traditions.
